唐代四大贤相之一。初唐时期从李世民征战四方，又参与谋划和发动“玄武门之变”，累功至尚书右仆射，封莱国公，佐太宗创“贞观之治”。与政治家房玄龄共掌朝政，史称：“玄龄多谋，如晦善断，当世语良相，常称房杜。”被誉为唐代四大贤相之一。\n\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1303_1808_1630_2198.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"16%\" /></div>\n\n\n杜审言（约646~708)：唐文学家、著名诗人。襄阳（今属湖北）人，迁居河南巩县。字必简。咸亨进士。曾任隰城尉、洛阳丞、吉州司户参军、膳部员外郎。官至修文馆直学士。与李峤、崔融、苏味道齐名，称“文章四友”。明人辑有《杜审言集》。\n\n杜甫（712~770年）：唐代伟大现实主义诗人。字子美，祖籍襄阳（今湖北襄樊襄\n\n# 渑池杜氏宗谱", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1276_1055_1637_1494.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//17b04831-5671-4649-8752-4450b1e72048/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1276_1055_1637_1494.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A26%3A42Z%2F-1%2F%2Fee9f99e7d829e237b025b1d05273ada29d1d7713493b4537fe89a17e8802053c", "imgs/img_in_image_box_1303_1808_1630_2198.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//17b04831-5671-4649-8752-4450b1e72048/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1303_1808_1630_2198.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A26%3A42Z%2F-1%2F%2F36833f7abf661989d7c0808c661e8762705853a02c4db34a8f34f671e7c33c3e"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//17b04831-5671-4649-8752-4450b1e72048/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A26%3A44Z%2F-1%2F%2Fac3969de9b242fe9205996c177f8754d9708140e33d6fe3150af26c8615950c8", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//17b04831-5671-4649-8752-4450b1e72048/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A26%3A44Z%2F-1%2F%2F439fe32c32f6fa072c9c298415c6e352e9bb651f853b881035d165aac9cbfdfe", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v